<br>
I'm sorry that your guild was cheated out of a warrior epic, Pala, but the same animosity does not warrant every occasion.<br>
<br>
There is no &quot;ganking&quot; if you're there first, you trigger first, and you engage first. I don't care how much you think your friends deserve the epic.<br>
<br>
&quot;Whatever guild ganks us will be put on our /who all lists and tracked 24/7, also our scout force ( very good one ) will ensure your guild is where we think you are. Whatever mob you engage will be ganked out from underneath you.&quot;<br>
<br>
Once again, there is no &quot;ganking&quot; if you engage first. But there is leapfrogging. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
